This is a grails plugins that allows you to write notes within your codes and tests. 
These can then be retrieved from the command line as follows:

grails code_notes

A note is written as follows:
//TODO: My note.

The note ends at the line break. No more colons are allowed in that line, if any are inserted, any content after those colons will be ignored.
These notes are inteded to be short and simple.
